snippet.title: Katz Play - Heist Gameplay
snippet.description:
ANSWER THE CALL… OF FUN.
Evade laser traps, water guns and cages. Stay clear of watchful cameras and seize the chance to take even the most outlandish of things as you search for the loot with your team of cats before the alarm goes off. There’ll be laughter aplenty!

Download the game in your mobile phone (IOS/Android)
https://bit.ly/Play-KATZ

https://discord.com/invite/katz
